    • getByOwner

      @GET @Produces({"application/json","application/yaml","application/xml"}) org.apache.syncope.common.lib.to.SAML2IdPMetadataTO getByOwner​(@QueryParam("appliesTo") @DefaultValue("Syncope") java.lang.String appliesTo)
      Returns a document outlining keys and metadata of Syncope as SAML 2.0 IdP.
      Parameters:
      appliesTo - indicates the SAML 2.0 IdP metadata document owner and applicability, where a value of 'Syncope' indicates the Syncope server as the global owner of the metadata and keys.
      Returns:
      SAML 2.0 IdP metadata
